The paper deals with a problem of online caching with dependencies, which is a classic problem in computer science and falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS). The specific application mentioned in the abstract is forwarding table optimization in IP routing and software-defined networks, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also presents a deterministic algorithm, which falls under the category of algorithms (cs.AL). The problem of caching with dependencies is also relevant in the context of system integration (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT).
